{"tid":420282,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 天份 定 努力較重要?","createTime":"2017-10-01T09:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T10:33:20.000Z","uid":87756,"like":220,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd7f5be8e93763a4dc00b50d1adcde018edbda2","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"天賦和努力，何者對成就<strong>比較</strong>重要??<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 梗係天賦喇仲洗問<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 只要有恆心鐵柱磨成針 <br />\n<br />\n投完睇下你有無「天才情意結」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cbV8nz-Lec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_cbV8nz-Lec&d=ZZTUqjObpp05G%2FEC0l3KCE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5618bed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cbV8nz-Lec</a>"},{"pid":"af76eaf8609918817b7398dcda721c502f6a58ad","tid":420282,"uid":86935,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起小李同我愛羅對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6fbbd2f5af338fdcdc191e04111d09af23b710","tid":420282,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天賦和努力，何者對成就<strong>比較</strong>重要??<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 梗係天賦喇仲洗問<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 只要有恆心鐵柱磨成針 <br />\n<br />\n投完睇下你有無「天才情意結」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cbV8nz-Lec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_cbV8nz-Lec&d=ZZTUqjObpp05G%2FEC0l3KCE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5618bed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cbV8nz-Lec</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n科學，策略，方法（後天），情商，智商（先天）先最重要<br />\n<br />\n後天重要，但唔係努力，而係策略。"},{"pid":"cae8e7b5f21aa76ebfc6e5a9c8d7bc9b36fa856d","tid":420282,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天賦和努力，何者對成就<strong>比較</strong>重要??<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 梗係天賦喇仲洗問<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 只要有恆心鐵柱磨成針 <br />\n<br />\n投完睇下你有無「天才情意結」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cbV8nz-Lec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_cbV8nz-Lec&d=ZZTUqjObpp05G%2FEC0l3KCE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5618bed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_cbV8nz-Lec</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n科學，策略，方法（後天），情商，智商（先天）先最重要<br />\n<br />\n後天重要，但唔係努力，而係策略。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀書都有學習的方法，讀書策略"},{"pid":"080efd04abf1ccf9f7874dbbf817cb19eb84a4b8","tid":420282,"uid":7326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻諗起小李同我愛羅對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次都睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cNTspQ5uUUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcNTspQ5uUUU&d=ZZTUqjObpp05G%2FEC0l3KCE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4b6c39ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cNTspQ5uUUU</a>"},{"pid":"df08047a10f01419d4b22d04fdeb3da6e3ceb4fc","tid":420282,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"努力重要"},{"pid":"a34af9ce9dec0aaa04e5eb9522d06b2759df16b9","tid":420282,"uid":33336,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:55:40.000Z","msg":"一個智障既人係無能力整火箭，即使佢好努力學習同研究"},{"pid":"face441dc6b73d5c2a941e31b8b80839d1d5711c","tid":420282,"uid":86935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即刻諗起小李同我愛羅對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次都睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cNTspQ5uUUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcNTspQ5uUUU&d=ZZTUqjObpp05G%2FEC0l3KCE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4b6c39ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cNTspQ5uUUU</a></blockquote><br />\n努力既天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aff7604211805f1cc86740de80c7ea5e58ae7a6","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618a91738ba3919ed41fe72bf8f795a06447bf3b","tid":420282,"uid":39081,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個智障既人係無能力整火箭，即使佢好努力學習同研究</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都身懷天賦，但如果用會不會爬樹的能力來評判一只魚，它會終其一生以為自己愚蠢。"},{"pid":"643aa78e35c4f746f22efbc31b5464bc75160b73","tid":420282,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個智障既人係無能力整火箭，即使佢好努力學習同研究</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都身懷天賦，但如果用會不會爬樹的能力來評判一只魚，它會終其一生以為自己愚蠢。</blockquote><br />\n現實就係咁,根本冇咁多資源去測試一個人"},{"pid":"d430f1c74002f36106eb8272bd87edd48e6a7f94","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個智障既人係無能力整火箭，即使佢好努力學習同研究</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都身懷天賦，但如果用會不會爬樹的能力來評判一只魚，它會終其一生以為自己愚蠢。</blockquote><br />\n現實就係咁,根本冇咁多資源去測試一個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/201120_4570cadcf2de67e85d984e2fab679ee0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F201120_4570cadcf2de67e85d984e2fab679ee0.jpg&h=014c77a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbee4a596a29820dbfdbf7ed3a7b7380d1220896","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"31714ae855909c7b0d2280588c7a3dfed14e30bf","tid":420282,"uid":67260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻諗起小李同我愛羅對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到個標題就諗起火易"},{"pid":"888622ec04e5ffa99f801fdc7dad5c7a0f5325eb","tid":420282,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4c5714c810869dc32df509cc05417c25fe2dee9","tid":420282,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"天份重要啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇天份唔會勁得去邊"},{"pid":"095fcb7cfb59917cb25fd3c4919d2430623a9265","tid":420282,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"一定係天分"},{"pid":"3313b2c733d368c3e68c9b15ccdddc2ae01688a0","tid":420282,"uid":149878,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"咁講<br />\n天賦=你去到有幾高,係你嘅天花板同幾易去到<br />\n努力=去天花板嘅過程"},{"pid":"f60fedb4a4657cbcfc81d17693f3dcbec66c5849","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁講<br />\n天賦=你去到有幾高,係你嘅天花板同幾易去到<br />\n努力=去天花板嘅過程</blockquote><br />\n呢個比喻幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca69e54ea4874fb62840a7ffc89c00639bf63a3","tid":420282,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁講<br />\n天賦=你去到有幾高,係你嘅天花板同幾易去到<br />\n努力=去天花板嘅過程</blockquote><br />\n呢個比喻幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯, 幾時都係天賦重要, 努力只係比一大班廢人中既小數份子去有朝一日,把握機會,賭贏左黎翻盤, 但係時也命也, 無人話得埋"},{"pid":"b90b5b4408a2b79dda9ad1a5c98e995b78723ebf","tid":420282,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"緊係天份重要<br />\n用online game比喻 天份=人地課金買時間<br />\n                                  努力=打餐死先追到人地<br />\n結果：人地只要努力多少少 你既努力就收得皮"},{"pid":"7297579d1ba1b58e3a4bce0869600818bfc3bf11","tid":420282,"uid":138613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"天才偏誤<br />\n英文term係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自己查下相關info<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eba14ef2e66b5c1093b095a769567db3513cb21","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天才偏誤<br />\n英文term係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自己查下相關info<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正式term :Naturalness bias"},{"pid":"5dab432d96d31d3db5b58978346bbb27f68606c3","tid":420282,"uid":92185,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"就好似外貌，天生生得靚既就個個都會讚；相反整容個d，其實佢地可能背後儲左好多錢，仲要受手術時既痛苦同風險先得到既美貌，俾人發現左就只會一面倒俾人話整容雞點點點<br />\n其實大家打從心底都係覺得先天比較重要"},{"pid":"93cbb66a49722b71cd808d66381c05e3b4d2ce4d","tid":420282,"uid":112742,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"努力係天份既一種 <br />\n或者咁講 個人有幾努力唔係咁易比較到<br />\n有人好努力先捱到每日溫兩個鐘書 又有人唔洗點逼已經每日溫四五粒鐘"},{"pid":"bc009e4f787bd84b19cfd8c6b021a76179d4a4df","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天才偏誤<br />\n英文term係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自己查下相關info<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正式term :Naturalness bias</blockquote><br />\n更正番，中文應該譯做天分偏誤，條片打錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92304a49aabe355c9e3ddf9a4877f40edd58ef2a","tid":420282,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:15:17.000Z","msg":"發明家做唔到物理學家<br />\n物理學家做唔到藝術家<br />\n藝術家做唔到語言學家<br />\n語言學家做唔到運動家<br />\n運動家做唔到以上學家<br />\n所以娃哈哈屌啦媽卡卡"},{"pid":"f76358e9d6db2105c0203a1a21ea5bffa38d887a","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發明家做唔到物理學家<br />\n物理學家做唔到藝術家<br />\n藝術家做唔到語言學家<br />\n語言學家做唔到運動家<br />\n運動家做唔到以上學家<br />\n所以娃哈哈屌啦媽卡卡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc03435c8a81a6caadd9382353bd15df92430e7d","tid":420282,"uid":86031,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"努力<br />\n<br />\n可能天份係容易令到一個人成功<br />\n如果你冇天份<br />\n就算你幾努力都冇可能追上果d一開始就好有天份嘅人<br />\n但做人其實唔係淨係求結果<br />\n學識享受努力嘅過程<br />\n先係做人最大嘅得著"},{"pid":"94d40e8c1a52ff6628a2a2dbd393a6867e583f8b","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a45df52e2d58882352193f42d21cbe33c624fba","tid":420282,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"有努力可以追過天份<br />\n但好多人係半路尋已經quit左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1607f030c56562c8497b65428c00352b5bc04c74","tid":420282,"uid":5322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"一定係努力<br />\n但能唔能夠努力做一件事，我覺得需要天賦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f320ce776eaec3c45bb90ad418ebd5c20effec","tid":420282,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁講<br />\n天賦=你去到有幾高,係你嘅天花板同幾易去到<br />\n努力=去天花板嘅過程</blockquote><br />\n呢個比喻幾好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯, 幾時都係天賦重要, 努力只係比一大班廢人中既小數份子去有朝一日,把握機會,賭贏左黎翻盤, 但係時也命也, 無人話得埋</blockquote><br />\n但係你有無諗過佢贏到都係天賦之一,總會有啲人係大器晚成"},{"pid":"30cdcf80cbcba9dc925804a3a2ce07c461010a3f","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2df6486288b21f1be28df760859752a3119a973f","tid":420282,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"若果想做一個好叻既人.天份重要d"},{"pid":"243d27da8ec98b0b1f972b3f2bfcf976e73fb7f2","tid":420282,"uid":77143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"肯定係天才仲要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你成個命題根本有問題<br />\n講到好似天才唔可以努力咁<br />\n<br />\n實際上講努力個個人都係咁上下咖啦<br />\n因為呢樣根本係係人都可以做到嘅野"},{"pid":"0530c552c5ba88b78f37f032dfdf3e4e8498fd37","tid":420282,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯定係天才重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你成個命題根本有問題<br />\n講到好似天才唔可以努力咁<br />\n<br />\n實際上講努力個個人都係咁上下咖啦<br />\n因為呢樣根本係係人都可以做到嘅野</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0b477a65a861c656515f6eaa6fda56bdd3a97944","tid":420282,"uid":56634,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:36:27.000Z","msg":"100%天份0%努力<br />\n同<br />\n100%努力0%天份<br />\n都係唔會成功"},{"pid":"4708c31becd98a8da82d47793cc9a2c7a9ecf701","tid":420282,"uid":46325,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"努力係基本但天份重要啲，只係大部分人都係未到要用天分分高低就賴鳩自己冇天份，但明明只係未努力過或者用錯方法"},{"pid":"d33f1def969dd4084c6353d9cee1bc71918e3860","tid":420282,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>100%天份0%努力<br />\n同<br />\n100%努力0%天份<br />\n都係唔會成功</blockquote><br />\n感覺有啲唔啱, 100%天份等於乜都識,我認為"},{"pid":"3870b9433728655c7bb9343b8e3eaf21294834b7","tid":420282,"uid":38462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:50:31.000Z","msg":"細個覺得努力<br />\n大個覺得天份"},{"pid":"44356740af130791db9bdcdfcb4ad51acb432ec3","tid":420282,"uid":89906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"天賦唔係努力可以彌補，唔好同我講咩將勤可以補拙，龜兔賽跑都要有隻懶訓嘅兔仔，懶惰嘅天才偷懶都可以事半功倍，而勤力嘅凡人，終其一生都只會庸碌無為，天道酬幸不酬勤，可以大放異彩嘅，就只有注定可以成功嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f633a50fd4ec76005c0a4555be51b84c79a077","tid":420282,"uid":47356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天賦唔係努力可以彌補，唔好同我講咩將勤可以補拙，龜兔賽跑都要有隻懶訓嘅兔仔，懶惰嘅天才偷懶都可以事半功倍，而勤力嘅凡人，終其一生都只會庸碌無為，天道酬幸不酬勤，可以大放異彩嘅，就只有注定可以成功嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nexactly, 努力如果好彩先可以僥倖勝利, 比你有天賦既人有心同你玩, 玩一百次你就輸一百次"},{"pid":"cd53f740ba84e3e7fcb5c722a0f6ac1cd604f605","tid":420282,"uid":120537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T22:59:11.000Z","msg":"中二話題就動漫台開啦"},{"pid":"c445f5f3f9521532e19ee49db3bad3004656bed0","tid":420282,"uid":36014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T23:00:56.000Z","msg":"本人相信優生學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06adbfd63add7e2bf4377562338273c1b2718438","tid":420282,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T23:03:45.000Z","msg":"美斯vs C朗"},{"pid":"ed7745c9d8063434551f5c6a611ba904aec12d4e","tid":420282,"uid":89906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T23:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天賦唔係努力可以彌補，唔好同我講咩將勤可以補拙，龜兔賽跑都要有隻懶訓嘅兔仔，懶惰嘅天才偷懶都可以事半功倍，而勤力嘅凡人，終其一生都只會庸碌無為，天道酬幸不酬勤，可以大放異彩嘅，就只有注定可以成功嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nexactly, 努力如果好彩先可以僥倖勝利, 比你有天賦既人有心同你玩, 玩一百次你就輸一百次</blockquote><br />\n鐵柱可以磨成針，但木頭只能夠磨成牙籤，當中表達左d咩大家心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c1f9f80330e2cdee5860538f84dc8bd59d2ab7","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中二話題就動漫台開啦</blockquote><br />\n有時間可以睇下 恆毅力 呢本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad78299e5eff809192ab962b8716773bced2780a","tid":420282,"uid":87756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯定係天才仲要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你成個命題根本有問題<br />\n講到好似天才唔可以努力咁<br />\n<br />\n實際上講努力個個人都係咁上下咖啦<br />\n因為呢樣根本係係人都可以做到嘅野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何者對成就 <strong>比較</strong> 重要<br />\n無否定天才唔可以努力"},{"pid":"8abb7133f2d904b4d2b4353a8aed1c6f6a4f0ce3","tid":420282,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個智障既人係無能力整火箭，即使佢好努力學習同研究</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都身懷天賦，但如果用會不會爬樹的能力來評判一只魚，它會終其一生以為自己愚蠢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個社會就係用呢個準則去睇人<br />\n除非你屋企好有錢 比你去搵專長<br />\n<br />\n其實有幾多個天才 <br />\n都只演活一個值萬幾蚊的文員<br />\n或者一個Sales佬"}]}